Attempts to create a valid wadl file from yml files

Goals: 

* Simplify creation of wadl files via yml and conventions
* Move back and forth between YML and XML seemlessly


Problems:

* Rails active support (or anything else) does not support this natively
* Attributes get munged into elements

Links:
